<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/28419597">如何理解和评价王曾“夫执政者，恩欲归己，怨使谁归？”这句话？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3550466" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">范仲淹尝问曾曰：“明扬士类，宰相之任也。公之盛德，独少此耳。”曾曰：“夫执政者，恩欲归己，怨使谁归?”仲淹服其言。<br>宋史王曾传。</div>


</div>
